{"tid":805432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[PRODUCE48] 排名順位個人感想","createTime":"2018-09-03T20:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T13:37:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"59b2ea5509d83d7cb6e5e07af7a678bc8d9be516","tid":805432,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T20:06:10.000Z","msg":"1.張元英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國狗自尊心極強 點都唔會比日本妹拎第一位<br />\n年紀得14 談吐唔太成熟 以一位黎對比一二季 差左幾千公里<br />\n<br />\n2.宮咲咲良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實力仍不足 <br />\n唔清楚先定後天 舞台既體質好強<br />\n<br />\n3.曹柔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑幕造票味超濃 個人非常反感 <span style=\"color: red;\">將會成為小妹新狙擊對像</span><br />\n張圭猁STONE MUSICH等人 原來只係成佢鋪路<br />\n由2選第18名 升到1選第3名 係安選之女<br />\n雖然次次降KEY唱 但D人好似聽唔出 有預感成為主唱<br />\n<br />\n4.崔藝娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n表情多多 舞蹈實力幾強<br />\n幾吸引觀眾眼球 係活力擔當<br />\n<br />\n5.安宥真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同同公司張元英比我自己比較喜歡安宥真<br />\n安宥真表情冇咁作狀 表情外貌都幾吸引<br />\n<br />\n6.矢吹奈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細細粒幾可愛 而且幾唱得<br />\n可以擔當主唱<br />\n<br />\n7.權恩菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對波好大 個人又幾搞笑<br />\n跳舞實力12個入面最強(個人認為)<br />\n幾次評審唔係C位都勁搶眼<br />\n<br />\n8.姜惠元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獨一無二既角色 吸引左好多人支持 連續排名都係TOP<br />\n但實力嚴重不足 有待加強<br />\n<br />\n9.本田仁美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n把聲好BB覺得佢唱歌唔係太好聽<br />\n相反舞蹈天份幾高 並唔輸比其他韓國練習生<br />\n<br />\n10.金彩媛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解又係冇神神爆左上黎<br />\n不過覺得佢個樣係韓國人既口味<br />\n<br />\n11.金珉周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n花樽 實力平平 完全靠個靚樣<br />\n<br />\n12.李彩燕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n領導力同跳舞實力唔輸比權恩菲 而且唱功都較強<br />\n擺明比人當狗撚 專登放去12位出道<br />\n而且離開左JYP 我會+多佢一分<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先追完 希望有人理下我<br />\nE季收視好似仆撚晒街 最後一集都相差好多<br />\n唔認為可以大紅大紫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18ee293d959d3170c1ba722b741e5e7edc88d22","tid":805432,"uid":12432,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T20:13:07.000Z","msg":"po去屌柒區啦，大把人理你"},{"pid":"883a698cdfa2f966fcf357b551d56b1c9b413964","tid":805432,"uid":96941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"有曹婦=隊野已經收左皮<br />\n樣衰到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea9b8a6ae84aa5ff5b75c857e58379f7b568091","tid":805432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:15:11.000Z","msg":"導清反曹柔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98025d04ef09b5a9ff3f6f76d40814600ddf1f0b","tid":805432,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c18ee293d959d3170c1ba722b741e5e7edc88d22","tid":805432,"uid":12432,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T20:13:07.000Z","msg":"po去屌柒區啦，大把人理你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"有幾條煩膠ON9當有趣 見到都唔想入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be42bf9fe84d500194edd768c91b7883bd20f9e5","tid":805432,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea9b8a6ae84aa5ff5b75c857e58379f7b568091","tid":805432,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:15:11.000Z","msg":"導清反曹柔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"一直都唔太LIKE佢<br />\n睇埋最後一集真係屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c24abc685179520e0922987208b421441dd430","tid":805432,"uid":183162,"like":0,"disli